name: Dali Rainbow Jasper Points
description:
Obsessed with the energy of this new Dali Rainbow Jasper Point! Comforting, healing, nurturing stone that connects with the root chakra to ground you. Protects your aura from negativity. This opaque stone is also known as a fancy jasper with its deep burgundy, brown and pink colors. Just gorgeous to look at!
Measures Approx 3-4" tall
